*Dokle* ćeš čekati? (How long will you wait?) 

Neka čeka *dokle* god zaželi. (Let her wait as long as she wants.)

On se trudi *dokle* god može. (He strives as long as he can.)

*Dokle* ću čekati da se pojaviš? (How long will I wait for you to appear?)

Ona se uspešno bori *dokle* god može. (She fights successfully as long as she can.)